Detailed Description

This header file contains identifiers and macros that can be used to access the Axi srio gen2 device. The driver APIs/functions are defined in xsrio.h.

Note:

MODIFICATION HISTORY:

Ver Who Date Changes ----- ---- -------- --------------------------------------------------------- 1.0 adk 16/04/14 Initial release.
